  <notes>
Completed 2026-06-30. End-to-end smoke deferred to operator T145 UAT (sandboxed agent has no browser to spaarkedev1; data mutation deferred to operator per CLAUDE.md §6 + Dataverse delete-record consent requirement).

Code-path verification + Dataverse data reads identified TWO deterministic bugs at the Dataverse data layer (no BFF code change required). See audit 123 §10 (newly appended Resolution section) for full diagnosis + recommended fix + scope analysis.

Disposition revised from "likely WORKING" (audit §5.1) → "NOT WORKING — deterministic failure." Audit §5.1 had ranked the EntityNameValidator risk as priority-2 ("stripping output"); T143 found the failure is actually "fails validation, kills entire run, returns empty" — total failure on every invocation.

Primary bug: node 3 "Entity Name Validator" (sprk_playbooknode c3c5226d-5b71-f111-ab0d-7ced8ddc4a05) has stub configJson lacking required candidateText + allowList. Wave 5 backfill (notes/drafts/playbook-node-review-output.csv:61) set executortype=141 by node-name match without verifying configJson contained executor-required inputs.

Secondary bug: node 2 "AI Analysis" (444b06d3-...) configJson has stub systemPrompt override that clobbers ACT-023's real prompt via PromptSchemaOverrideMerger.

Recommended minimal fix is data-layer only (Dataverse Web API or Power Apps Maker edit). Operator applies §10.4 fixes A + B; then T145 UAT can validate end-to-end against Matter + WA together (per §10.5 inheritance).

Sweep query for other EntityNameValidator orphans returned 2 rows: the Matter node (broken) + Daily Briefing ValidateEntityNames (healthy per Wave 11 T116). No further EntityNameValidator orphans exist; scope of cleanup confirmed limited.

T144 (WA wizard) recommendation: WA reuses /api/workspace/matters/pre-fill (audit §1.3). Once Matter §10.4 fix is in, WA AI-prefill path is automatically restored. T144 should be a straightforward verify-and-UAT task — confirm operator has applied Matter fix, then UAT WA at T145 alongside Matter. No separate playbook or fix needed for WA.

Commit: df0dd01ae on work/spaarke-ai-platform-unification-r7.
  </notes>
